            <header class="entry-header">
                <h1 class="entry-title">You&#039;ve entered uncharted waters</h1>
            </header><!-- .entry-header -->
            <div class="entry-content">
                                <blockquote>
                    For certain, you have to be lost to find a place that can’t be found, elseways everyone would know where it was.</br><em>Captain Barbossa</em>                </blockquote>
